{"word":"G531 - ἀπαράβατος - aparábatos - ap-ar-ab'-at-os - Unchangeable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπαράβατος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aparábatos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-ar-ab'-at-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unchangeable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மாறிப்போகாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unchangeable, untransferable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3845 - παραβαίνω - parabaínō - par-ab-ah'-ee-no/3845\">G3845</a>; <i>not passing away</i>, that is, <i>untransferable</i> (perpetual): - unchangeable.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3845/3845\">G3845</a>, <a href=\"#/G3847/3847\">G3847</a>, <a href=\"#/G3848/3848\">G3848</a>, <a href=\"#/G5233/5233\">G5233</a>, <a href=\"#/G531/531\">G531</a>"}]}